              <li>└─ <a href="https://github.com/solcoder/SolCoder/blob/main/LICENSE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-solana-purple hover:text-solana-green transition-colors">Full License on GitHub</a></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Contributing -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl text-solana-green font-bold mb-4">└─ Contributing to SolCoder</h2>
            <p>
              By contributing to SolCoder, you agree that your contributions will be licensed under the MIT License. We encourage contributions from the community to make SolCoder better for everyone.
            </p>
          </section>
